# Adversary fixture: FM1 — wrong TriX namespace URI
# Hypothesis: a parser that validates the xmlns declaration will reject this
#   document because "http://www.w3.org/2004/03/trix/trix-1" (no trailing
#   slash) is not the canonical TriX namespace
#   "http://www.w3.org/2004/03/trix/trix-1/". The two URIs are distinct;
#   the document is not a valid TriX document.
# Expected outcome: reject
outcome: reject
fact-count: 0
divergence-hypothesis: AcceptRejectSplit — namespace-oblivious XML parsers that
  do not validate the xmlns value against the canonical TriX namespace will
  accept the document and produce 1 fact; conformant parsers reject it.
spec-ref: TriX spec §2 (HPL-2004-56) — document element must be <TriX> in
  namespace http://www.w3.org/2004/03/trix/trix-1/ (with trailing slash)
